<div style="margin-left: 3em;"><a href="#toc2">Being picky</a></div>
<div style="margin-left: 3em;"><a href="#toc3">Social engineering</a></div>
<div style="margin-left: 3em;"><a href="#toc4">Posting to the site</a></div>
<div style="margin-left: 3em;"><a href="#toc5">Closing notes</a></div>
</div>
